                <section name="Read Me">
                    <subsection name="Required Configuration">
                        <p> 
                              Nabla has been developed using the J2EE specifications for web application.
                              The following configuration is needed to run Nabla :
                            
                        </p>
                        <p>
                        <ul>
                              <li>A Java Virtual Machine(1.6.x or greater) must be installed on your Operating System</li>
                              <li>A Servlet engine which is compatible with the API 2.2 (Apache Tomcat is recommanded)</li>
                              <li>A Relational Database (Default configuration is Derby). </li>
                        </ul>
                        </p>
                    </subsection>
